<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak yoshoba moma
 Hina hanta foyukʋt
 Il a̱yashke, aiahnit
 Hʋsh anukfinlashke.

[V2]
 Hina hanta achukma
 A̱ya la chi̱ pullashke;
 Moma kʋt siakaiya
 Pullakbano, ahni li.

[V3]
 Ʋbanumpuli puta
 Chu̱kʋsh a̱hli hokʋto,
 Chisʋs a binili ka
 Ona pulla hi oke.

[V4]
 Hatak pin tikba hokʋt
 Illit pin taiyaha tok;
 Pishno kia, e moma kʋt
 Pilla chi̱ ak inlishke.

[V5]
 Pi okcha̱ya ta̱kla 'k osh,
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla ka,
 Pi chu̱kʋsh a̱ mominchit
 Pit il ema pullashke.

[V6]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla ka,
 Pi chu̱kʋsh a̱ mominchit
 Isht im ilbʋsha fehnʋt,
 Iloh im asilhhashke.</lyrics>
<title>Hatak yoshoba moma ƲIT14</title>
<time_sig>7.7.7.7.</time_sig>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<hymn_number>14</hymn_number>
</song>